'''Ironman's Bay''' is a large area of water off the west coast of [[Westeros]]. The bay is formed by the Flint Cliffs and [[Cape Kraken]] in the north, the [[Cape of Eagles]] to the east and the north coast of the [[Westerlands]] to the south. The coastlands of the [[North]], the [[Riverlands]] and the Westerlands all border the bay.

Most famously, the bay contains the [[Iron Islands]], and its waters are controlled by the [[Iron Fleet]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season1/#!/locations/pyke/ HBO viewers guide, season 1 map, Pyke entry]&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season2/#!/locations/pyke/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 map, Pyke entry]&lt;/ref&gt;
